{"tid":320382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心情不好想請假　老闆：你是全公司的榜樣","createTime":"2017-07-13T13:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T15:27:12.000Z","uid":78785,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"213faa2147e3796c1097bea85fe9c449dd8c4fb0","tid":320382,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgapiv2.nownews.com/?h=545&amp;q=70&amp;src=https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/59659164a2c2676982340e2c_201707121103.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgapiv2.nownews.com%2F%3Fh%3D545%26q%3D70%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F59659164a2c2676982340e2c_201707121103.png&h=62576666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5965916483bc8d69889a0449_201707121103.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5965916483bc8d69889a0449_201707121103.png&h=748504a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲瑪達琳以保養精神健康為由向公司請假。（圖／翻攝自boredpanda）<br />\n「請假」絕對是上班族最有感的名詞之一，請假名目百百種，病假、事假、公假、育嬰假、婚喪假等，其中，「病假」幾乎可以說是上班族最常行使的一種請假權利，同時，在如何定義病假上又會衍伸出許多問題。國外就有一名網頁設計師，以心情狀況不佳要「保養精神健康」為由，向老闆請病假，但老闆的回應卻出乎大家意料。<br />\n<br />\n這名網頁設計師名叫瑪達琳（Madalyn Parker），來自美國密西根，在一家名叫Olark的公司工作，日前，她因為覺得自己需要幾天的時間來恢復她的精神健康，因此寄信給老闆以及同事請病假，信中也提到，希望她下周來上班時，可以以全新的狀態來公司上班。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲瑪達琳以保養精神健康為由向公司請假。（圖／翻攝自boredpanda）<br />\n<br />\n但出乎意料的是，老闆不但沒有生氣，甚至嘉許她的行為，在回信給瑪達琳的內容裡，不只感謝她寄來這封信，甚至謝謝她提醒了自己，原來除了感冒等的生理不適，精神狀態上的心理不適也可以成為請病假的理由，也表示不敢相信這項規定居然沒有被列入公司守則當中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5965916415c74c69bf7e8abc_201707121103.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5965916415c74c69bf7e8abc_201707121103.png&h=59a5850f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲老闆的回覆出乎意料。（圖／翻攝自boredpanda）<br />\n<br />\n瑪琳達將請假信以及老闆的回覆上傳至自己的推特與大家分享，立即獲得許多關注，有的網友大力讚揚老闆的回覆，但也有網友抱持反面意見：「這對我來說，就跟明明沒生病卻謊稱生病要請假一樣。」、「例行休假不就是用來保養精神健康的嗎？為什麼要使用病假？」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/596591657a840a69b9284811_201707121103.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F596591657a840a69b9284811_201707121103.png&h=b0c34768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲瑪達琳在自己的推特上發布照片，告訴大家她如何使用這幾天的病假。（圖／翻攝自boredpanda）"},{"pid":"bb360c6f2bc452e35a57bb78e671a38de5f46e46","tid":320382,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"應該有個壓力指標，過左標準就可以放假"},{"pid":"38600b5204d80b479ac89a6961a0f287ffd148ee","tid":320382,"uid":895,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"香港老闆：以後你可以日日休息"},{"pid":"167d29ffee2d2fcd0c981ccf718812fd3d1672bd","tid":320382,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"係咪串緊佢唔挨得昨"},{"pid":"64c93242f85a7a7bb4e26230162ef05338fa6890","tid":320382,"uid":38462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港老闆：以後你可以日日休息</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d8a8f2617f17c68ccc59a5bdff487c3e081679","tid":320382,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該有個壓力指標，過左標準就可以放假</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n思古井<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4257998f39cf4c33b984173e07f30379451be502","tid":320382,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪串緊佢唔挨得昨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真，頭先tbb都有報<br />\n<br />\n不過如果佢係一個大肥婆或者係男人就唔知請唔請到了"},{"pid":"19b70b2854cc8725e878d15e4c60f64500dcef55","tid":320382,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:38